<link href="adcp.css" rel="stylesheet"><entry><xh5>classic play • classical play</xh5><p> <i>classic play—</i>a play that serves as a standard; one that has come to be regarded as one of the best: Molly has a dream of acting in a <u>classic play</u>, but all the parts she likes are written for men.</p><p><i>classical play—</i>a play which is Roman or ancient Greek: A <u>classical play</u> (ancient Greek drama or work of a classical writer) is presented during the summer in cultural events held by municipalities.</p></entry>
